ove to New York, live cheaply and make the new art, music, and culture. These days Williamsburg has that special chemistry of the New York that's constantly renewing itself.                 NaN                 NaN                   NaN                 t                 NaN                  1.0                        NaN                 NaN                    t                      t            NaN           Williamsburg                     Brooklyn  40.709350 -73.953420           Entire rental unit  Entire home/apt             3        1.0          1 bath       2.0   1.0                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           ["Bed linens", "Hot water", "Fire extinguisher", "Dishwasher", "Microwave", "Oven", "Kitchen", "Free street parking", "Washer", "Hair dryer", "Extra pillows and blankets", "Air conditioning", "Iron", "Wifi", "Carbon monoxide alarm", "Dishes and silverware", "Stove", "Coffee maker", "Heating", "TV", "Smoke alarm", "Cooking basics", "Refrigerator", "Hangers", "Essentials", "Shampoo"]  117.27               2026-12-20                2027-01-19                  3518.00                       117.27                                                                                                                                        {"quote": {"taxes": null, "currency": "USD", "date_match": null, "service_fee": null, "total_price": "3518", "cleaning_fee": null, "is_available": true, "d